overview:
Nabbesh is a virtual Skills Marketplace targeting the Middle East and North Africa region.

Nabbesh connects skilled individuals whether in technology, arts, finance, business or education, to name a few with project based work opportunities. Nabbesh is a platform which provides employers with an access to a readily available talent pool from the Middle East and North Africa.

Individuals can create a free account on Nabbesh and list their skills along with a description and supporting material. People can use Nabbesh as a personal showcase and as a channel to promote themselves and find opportunities that suits theirs lifestyles and needs.

Employers can create free accounts on Nabbesh and post jobs. Employers will be able to browse thousands of individual accounts and connect with people directly. Employers will also be able to pay and rate different users after completing a job, this creates a transparent environment where only top individuals are rewarded for their efforts.
